0589726725e-29, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 276, \"end\": 298, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/6th_arrondissement_of_Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0923111316652257e-47, \"text\": \"Saint-Germain-des-Pr\\u00e9s\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/6th_arrondissement_of_Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/6th_arrondissement_of_Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this intrepid reporter\", \"from\": 189, \"to\": 211}, {\"ngram\": \"a table\", \"from\": 231, \"to\": 238}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact, no reservations are needed across Paris as the mix of negative headlines and pre-Games hype is keeping away the hordes during theseParis Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 303, \"to\": 463, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 346, \"end\": 351, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9269250589726725e-29, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fact\", \"from\": 306, \"to\": 310}, {\"ngram\": \"no reservations\", \"from\": 312, \"to\": 327}, {\"ngram\": \"the mix\", \"from\": 355, \"to\": 362}, {\"ngram\": \"negative headlines\", \"from\": 366, \"to\": 384}, {\"ngram\": \"pre-Games hype\", \"from\": 389, \"to\": 403}, {\"ngram\": \"the hordes\", \"from\": 420, \"to\": 430}, {\"ngram\": \"theseParis Olympic Games\", \"from\": 438, \"to\": 462}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hard-core sports fans are piling and there are big crowds for major events, including this weekend'sroad race time trialandmountain bike races, but several venues are seeing empty seats.\", \"from\": 465, \"to\": 651, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hard-core sports fans\", \"from\": 465, \"to\": 486}, {\"ngram\": \"big crowds\", \"from\": 512, \"to\": 522}, {\"ngram\": \"major events\", \"from\": 527, \"to\": 539}, {\"ngram\": \"this weekend'sroad race time trialandmountain bike races\", \"from\": 551, \"to\": 607}, {\"ngram\": \"several venues\", \"from\": 613, \"to\": 627}, {\"ngram\": \"empty seats\", \"from\": 639, \"to\": 650}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris is devoid of the masses of summer tourists who typically clog the City of Light every July and August.\", \"from\": 653, \"to\": 761, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 653, \"end\": 658, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9269250589726725e-29, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the masses\", \"from\": 672, \"to\": 682}, {\"ngram\": \"summer tourists\", \"from\": 686, \"to\": 701}, {\"ngram\": \"the City\", \"from\": 721, \"to\": 729}, {\"ngram\": \"Light\", \"from\": 733, \"to\": 738}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's not to say there are no tourists, but there are certainly a lot less than normal.\", \"from\": 763, \"to\": 851, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no tourists\", \"from\": 791, \"to\": 802}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are no long ticket lines at Mus\\u00e9e d'Orsay, and no waiting list for a lunchtime table at Les Deux Magots.\", \"from\": 853, \"to\": 963, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 887, \"end\": 900, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mus\\u00e9e_d'Orsay\", \"score\": 0.9999999943702278, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mus\\u00e9e d'Orsay\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q33506\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mus\\u00e9e_d'Orsay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mus\\u00e9e_d'Orsay\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no long ticket lines\", \"from\": 863, \"to\": 883}, {\"ngram\": \"no waiting list\", \"from\": 906, \"to\": 921}, {\"ngram\": \"a lunchtime table\", \"from\": 926, \"to\": 943}, {\"ngram\": \"Les Deux Magots\", \"from\": 947, \"to\": 962}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The metro and RER lines are quiet and it's easy to zip around the city by bike.\", \"from\": 964, \"to\": 1043, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 978, \"end\": 981, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RER_C\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 5.44306813632392e-13, \"text\": \"RER\", \"types\": [\"Q728937\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RER_C\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RER_C\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The metro\", \"from\": 964, \"to\": 973}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 1026, \"to\": 1034}, {\"ngram\": \"bike\", \"from\": 1038, \"to\": 1042}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Tr\\u00e8s dommage!\\\"\", \"from\": 1045, \"to\": 1060, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\\"Tr\\u00e8s dommage\", \"from\": 1045, \"to\": 1058}]}, {\"sentence\": \"said a taxi driver Sunday morning.\", \"from\": 1061, \"to\": 1095, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a taxi driver\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1079}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Normally in summer we are booked one day in advance, now we are all waiting 30 minutes for a fare.\\\"\", \"from\": 1096, \"to\": 1196, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"summer\", \"from\": 1109, \"to\": 1115}, {\"ngram\": \"advance\", \"from\": 1141, \"to\": 1148}, {\"ngram\": \"a fare\", \"from\": 1188, \"to\": 1194}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That lament echoes across Paris' typically tourist-swamped Left Bank.\", \"from\": 1198, \"to\": 1267, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1224, \"end\": 1229, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9269250589726725e-29, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1257, \"end\": 1266, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rive_Gauche\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.3937314205867e-42, \"text\": \"Left Bank\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rive_Gauche\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rive_Gauche\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That lament\", \"from\": 1198, \"to\": 1209}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tables on the terraces of the Rue de Buci were sitting empty on a Saturday night, and museums and top tourist sites have plenty of same-day tickets.\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1417, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tables\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1275}, {\"ngram\": \"the terraces\", \"from\": 1279, \"to\": 1291}, {\"ngram\": \"the Rue de Buci\", \"from\": 1295, \"to\": 1310}, {\"ngram\": \"a Saturday night\", \"from\": 1333, \"to\": 1349}, {\"ngram\": \"museums\", \"from\": 1355, \"to\": 1362}, {\"ngram\": \"top tourist sites\", \"from\": 1367, \"to\": 1384}, {\"ngram\": \"plenty\", \"from\": 1390, \"to\": 1396}, {\"ngram\": \"same-day tickets\", \"from\": 1400, \"to\": 1416}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The normally busy streets from Le Marais to the Arc de Triomphe are eerily quiet.\", \"from\": 1419, \"to\": 1500, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1467, \"end\": 1482, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arc_de_Triomphe\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7291942745207882e-29, \"text\": \"Arc de Triomphe\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arc_de_Triomphe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arc_de_Triomphe\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The normally busy streets\", \"from\": 1419, \"to\": 1444}, {\"ngram\": \"Le Marais\", \"from\": 1450, \"to\": 1459}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Everyone left the city if they could and the tourists are scared to come,\\\" said one hotel receptionist.\", \"from\": 1502, \"to\": 1606, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Everyone\", \"from\": 1503, \"to\": 1511}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 1517, \"to\": 1525}, {\"ngram\": \"the tourists\", \"from\": 1544, \"to\": 1556}, {\"ngram\": \"one hotel receptionist\", \"from\": 1583, \"to\": 1605}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are normally booked solid all summer, now we have free rooms during the Olympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 1607, \"to\": 1693, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"free rooms\", \"from\": 1661, \"to\": 1671}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1679, \"to\": 1691}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the same in nearly every Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 1695, \"to\": 1739, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"nearly every Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1712, \"to\": 1738}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pre-Games hype sends a bolt of fear among the locals and scares away tourists who expect lockdowns, security checks, road closures, and traffic jams.\", \"from\": 1741, \"to\": 1890, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Pre-Games hype\", \"from\": 1741, \"to\": 1755}, {\"ngram\": \"a bolt\", \"from\": 1762, \"to\": 1768}, {\"ngram\": \"fear\", \"from\": 1772, \"to\": 1776}, {\"ngram\": \"the locals\", \"from\": 1783, \"to\": 1793}, {\"ngram\": \"tourists\", \"from\": 1810, \"to\": 1818}, {\"ngram\": \"lockdowns\", \"from\": 1830, \"to\": 1839}, {\"ngram\": \"security checks\", \"from\": 1841, \"to\": 1856}, {\"ngram\": \"road closures\", \"from\": 1858, \"to\": 1871}, {\"ngram\": \"traffic jams\", \"from\": 1877, \"to\": 1889}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And a lot of that is true.\", \"from\": 1892, \"to\": 1918, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1896, \"to\": 1901}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Eiffel Tower is closed off to tourists, and many of Paris' top attractions have been converted into sports venues, including the Place de la Concorde, Gran Palais, Les Invalides, and the area around the Trocad\\u00e9ro and the Eiffel Tower.\", \"from\": 1920, \"to\": 2158, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1976, \"end\": 1981, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9269250589726725e-29, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2053, \"end\": 2073, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.616980672994936e-40, \"text\": \"Place de la Concorde\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\"}, {\"begin\": 2088, \"end\": 2101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Les_Invalides\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.914259141892147e-65, \"text\": \"Les Invalides\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Les_Invalides\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Les_Invalides\"}, {\"begin\": 2127, \"end\": 2136, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trocad\\u00e9ro\", \"score\": 0.9730907954876998, \"rank\": 0.023351147168026228, \"text\": \"Trocad\\u00e9ro\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trocad\\u00e9ro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trocad\\u00e9ro\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 1920, \"to\": 1936}, {\"ngram\": \"tourists\", \"from\": 1954, \"to\": 1962}, {\"ngram\": \"sports venues\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2037}, {\"ngram\": \"Gran Palais\", \"from\": 2075, \"to\": 2086}, {\"ngram\": \"the area\", \"from\": 2107, \"to\": 2115}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 2141, \"to\": 2157}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some of the famed bridges over the River Seine are also closed, including the gold-fringed Pont Alexandre III and others, but most have re-opened after the opening ceremony Friday night.\", \"from\": 2160, \"to\": 2346, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2195, \"end\": 2206, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}, {\"begin\": 2251, \"end\": 2269, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pont_Alexandre_III\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pont Alexandre III\", \"types\": [\"Q12280\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pont_Alexandre_III\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pont_Alexandre_III\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the famed bridges\", \"from\": 2168, \"to\": 2185}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 2274, \"to\": 2280}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 2312, \"to\": 2332}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The entire city center of Paris along both sides of the Seine, roughly from the Eiffel Tower to Notre Dame, was on a multi-down restricted zone that was open only to residents or hotel guests.\", \"from\": 2348, \"to\": 2540, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2374, \"end\": 2379, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9269250589726725e-29, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2404, \"end\": 2409, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.584819842817877e-37, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The entire city center\", \"from\": 2348, \"to\": 2370}, {\"ngram\": \"both sides\", \"from\": 2386, \"to\": 2396}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 2424, \"to\": 2440}, {\"ngram\": \"Notre Dame\", \"from\": 2444, \"to\": 2454}, {\"ngram\": \"a multi-down restricted zone\", \"from\": 2463, \"to\": 2491}, {\"ngram\": \"residents\", \"from\": 2514, \"to\": 2523}, {\"ngram\": \"hotel guests\", \"from\": 2527, \"to\": 2539}]}, {\"sentence\": \"More than 44,000 ugly metal barriers were put up in Paris this week as part of massive security preparations ahead of the Olympics, which formally kicked off yesterday.Locals are not thrilled.\\ud83d\\udd17https://t.co/Knpj7Ic05Ypic.twitter.com/FCptREAViP That's since been lifted, but a strong police presence remains high across the city as officials are clamping down to try to avoid any risk of a terrorist attack or political disturbances.\", \"from\": 2542, \"to\": 2976, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2594, \"end\": 2599, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9269250589726725e-29, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"More than 44,000 ugly metal barriers\", \"from\": 2542, \"to\": 2578}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 2613, \"to\": 2617}, {\"ngram\": \"massive security preparations\", \"from\": 2621, \"to\": 2650}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2660, \"to\": 2672}, {\"ngram\": \"Locals\", \"from\": 2710, \"to\": 2716}, {\"ngram\": \"a strong police presence\", \"from\": 2815, \"to\": 2839}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 2860, \"to\": 2868}, {\"ngram\": \"officials\", \"from\": 2872, \"to\": 2881}, {\"ngram\": \"any risk\", \"from\": 2916, \"to\": 2924}, {\"ngram\": \"a terrorist attack\", \"from\": 2928, \"to\": 2946}, {\"ngram\": \"political disturbances\", \"from\": 2950, \"to\": 2972}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So far, things have been very quiet.\", \"from\": 2978, \"to\": 3014, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 2986, \"to\": 2992}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What's keeping fans away?\", \"from\": 3016, \"to\": 3041, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 3031, \"to\": 3035}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the run-up to the Paris Games, hotel prices were marked up dramatically, with rooms going for $900 a night and more during the key Olympic dates between July 26 and August 11. Business travelers as well as tourists are staying away, either rescheduling meetings or going to nearby Spain or Italy instead.\", \"from\": 3043, \"to\": 3351, \"entities\": [{\"